{"type": "article", "id": 8049, "title": "J.Crew & Bulova 手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-02T07:44:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052346571myTwAjlEbxDzIi6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t美国时尚品牌J.Crew 最近联手表商 Bulova 推出了一款新的手表，Bulova 目前是美国历史最为悠久的手表制造商。这款作品的灵感来源是上个世纪 40 年代军用手表，采用白色表盘和绿色表带的搭配，帆布的材质看上去时尚而又充满活力。但目前定价是 199 美元，<a href=\"https://www.jcrew.com/hk/index.jsp?bmUID=kyiYsIT&amp;bmLocale=en_HK?srcCode=DI%7CHK%7CFL14%7CHB&amp;utm_source=Magalog&amp;utm_medium=Display&amp;utm_content=FLINTL14&amp;utm_campaign=DIWCMPG&amp;noPopUp=true\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234655QsEGk2ZhJf97AIOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234655JXj1s73TqEZGv2en.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234656lPsJKaRuGIg29NOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}